version_description: This version tries to capture the unique voicings and walk up/downs in the album version of the song.
Song in full, all lyrics chords and parts.

This is "Brother's Keeper" the iTunes Bonus track for Aimee Mann's 2012 album "Charmer". The song is in the key of Eb but is easiest to play in the key of C with a capo on the 3rd fret. This was created by ear so some chords may be simplified. I recommend toggling between Am and Am7 at the end of each bar (just lift up your finger and hammer it back down before the next verse). If you can play the F chord with your thumb on the low E string and the standard F7 shape, I highly recommend it to make this song very easy to play.
